{"lemma":"سَرِيَّة","slug":"سَرِيَّة","root":"س.ر.#","root_slug":"س-ر-_","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ر-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n19433","n19657","n19434","n19675","n19676","n19677","n19680"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"concubine, chivese"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"company"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"secrecy, discretion"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"feminine singular of سِرِّيّ (sirriyy)","tags":["feminine","form-of","singular"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From سِرّ • (sirr) m."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n19433","headword_ar":"سُرِّيَّةٌ","root":"sr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A concubine-slave; a female slave whom"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one takes as a possession and for concubitus;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a female slave to whom one assigns a house, or chamber, in which he lodges her,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and whom he takes as a possession and for concubitus:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuEoliy~apN","text_ar":"فُعْلِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Mgh, Msb,) from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sir~N","text_ar":"سِرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as signifying “ concubitus, ” (S, M, * Mgh, Msb, K,) or as signifying “ concealment, ” because a man often conceals and protects her from his wife; (S;) altered from the regular form of a rel. n., (S, M, Msb, K,) by its having damm [in the place of kesr]; (S, Msb;) for the rel. n. is sometimes thus altered, as in the instances of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duhoriY~N","text_ar":"دُهْرِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~ahoru","text_ar":"الدَّهْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suholiY~N","text_ar":"سُهْلِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^aroDu Als~aholapu","text_ar":"الاَرْضُ السَّهْلَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or it is with damm to distinguish it from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sir~iy~apN","text_ar":"سِرِّيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is applied to “ a free woman with whom one has sexual intercourse secretly, ” (Msb,) or “ one who prostitutes herself: ” (TA:) or it is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sur~N","text_ar":"سُرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suruwrN","text_ar":"سُرُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; because her owner rejoices in her; (Akh, * S, * Msb;) and if so, it is agreeable with analogy: (Msb:) so says A Heyth; and this is the best that has been said respecting it: (TA:) or it is of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuE~uwlapN","text_ar":"فُعُّولَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sarowN","text_ar":"سَرْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, Mgh,) the latter"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"being changed into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"for euphony, and then the [other]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"being incorporated into it and thus becoming"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"like it, after which the dammeh is changed into a kesreh because the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"is next to it: (M:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saraAriY~u","text_ar":"سَرَارِىُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, S, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saraArK","text_ar":"سَرَارٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (ISk, TA;) the latter, by poetic license. (Ham p. 304.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","M","Mgh","Msb","ISk"]},{"entry_id":"n19657","headword_ar":"سُرِّيَّةٌ","root":"srw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", said by some to be originally of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuE~uwlapN","text_ar":"فُعُّولَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sarowN","text_ar":"سَرْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sr","text_ar":"سر"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n19434","headword_ar":"سِرِّيَّةٌ","root":"sr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A free woman with whom one has sexual intercourse secretly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA, *) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who prostitutes herself:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) distinguished from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sur~iy~apN","text_ar":"سُرِّيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (Msb, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA"]},{"entry_id":"n19675","headword_ar":"سَرْيَةٌ","root":"srY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suroyapN","text_ar":"سُرْيَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"are inf. ns. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saraY","text_ar":"سَرَى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) or have a more special signification than the inf. n. of that verb, which is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saroYN","text_ar":"سَرْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sarayonaA saroyapF mina All~ayoli","text_ar":"سَرَيْنَا سَرْيَةً مِنَ اللَّيْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suroyapF","text_ar":"سُرْيَةً","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We journeyed by night a journey of the night"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and the pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suroyapN","text_ar":"سُرْيَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is [said to be]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"surFY","text_ar":"سُرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) or one says,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1356},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sarayonaA saroyapF waAHidapF","text_ar":"سَرَيْنَا سَرْيَةً وَاحِدَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We journeyed by night a single night-journey"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and the subst. [signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a journeying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"travelling, by night,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the night,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suroyapN","text_ar":"سُرْيَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"surFY","text_ar":"سُرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["M","K","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n19676","headword_ar":"سُرْيَةٌ","root":"srY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph, in four places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n19677","headword_ar":"سِرْيَةٌ","root":"srY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An arrow-head,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, M, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is small, short, round and smooth, having no breadth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA,) is a dial. var. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sirowapN","text_ar":"سِرْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.], (As, TA,) or formed from the latter word by the substitution of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"because of the kesreh: (M, TA:) accord. to the K, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sariy~apN","text_ar":"سَرِيَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a small round arrow-head;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but this is a mistake; the correct word being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siroyapN","text_ar":"سِرْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with kesr, and without teshdeed to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A2-  It is also a dial. var. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sirowapN","text_ar":"سِرْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"locust in its first state, when it is a larva."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"srw","text_ar":"سرو"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["As","M","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n19680","headword_ar":"سَرِيَّةٌ","root":"srY","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A portion of an army:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb:) of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEiylapN","text_ar":"فَعِيلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAEilapN","text_ar":"فَاعِلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; because marching by night, privily; (Mgh, Msb;) thus originally, and afterwards applied also to such as march by day: (Ham p. 45:) or it may be from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAisotiraA='u","text_ar":"الاِسْتِرَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"“ the act of choosing, or selecting; ” because a company chosen from the army: (Mgh: [but if so, belonging to art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"srw","text_ar":"سرو"},{"kind":"text","text":":])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from five persons to three hundred:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"four hundred:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of horsemen, about four hundred:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or the best thereof, (S,) or the utmost, (Nh,) consists of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"four hundred:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Nh:) or, accord. to the “ Fet-h el-Bári, ”"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from a hundred to five hundred:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nine,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"more than this;"},{"kind":"text","text":"three, and four, and the like being termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaliyEapN","text_ar":"طَلِيعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", not"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sariy~apN","text_ar":"سَرِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": but it is related of the Prophet that he sent"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a single person"},{"kind":"text","text":"as a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sariy~ap","text_ar":"سَرِيَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saraAyaA","text_ar":"سَرَايَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sariy~aAtN","text_ar":"سَرِيَّاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siroyapN","text_ar":"سِرْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","M","K","Nh","TA","Mgh"]}]}}